rComments: Cara was nice enough.  After I finished the class, I was irritated with the assignments and didn't think I'd gotten that much out of them. However, I took the class 2 years ago, and I use some of the things she mentioned in my tutoring sessions.

class is a 2 unit internship for cal teach and i highly recommend doing it regardless of the teacher.  she is nice enough, though her materials are not as helpful as i'd hoped. she often gave us assumptive assignments that asked us to look at race and gender is less constructive ways.  however, the class is really easy and the internship is fun
